org.datavec.api.berkeley

Class Iterators.IteratorIterator<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.datavec.api.berkeley.Iterators.IteratorIterator<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.Iterator<T>
    Enclosing class:
    Iterators

    public static class Iterators.IteratorIterator<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Iterator<T>
    Wraps a two-level iteration scenario in an iterator. Each key of the keys iterator returns an iterator (via the factory) over T's. The IteratorIterator loops through the iterator associated with each key until all the keys are used up.
